text: Van Wyck is an unincorporated community in Whatcom County, in the U.S. state of Washington. ==History== A post office called Van Wyck was established in 1891, and remained in operation until 1904. The community has the name of Alexander Van Wyck. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Whatcom County, Washington Category:Unincorporated communities in Washington (state)
title: Van Wyck, Washington
